    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable transportation option for someone looking for a functional car at a more accessible price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car has accumulated high mileage and shows visible signs of wear and tear both inside and out. You may notice some minor cosmetic blemishes and the vehicle will likely require some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near future to keep it running optimally. It\u2019s a solid choice for a daily driver if you\u2019re willing to put in a little effort to maintain it.",
